high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black chair then step to your right and walk to the wall then turn left and take a step to the black table.
Pick up the potato that's in front of you to the right of the plant.
Turn left and step to your left then walk to the counter then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your let to face the garbage.
Put the potato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the round table
Pick up a potato on the round table
Turn left then go the fridge
Open the fridge chill the potato take it out then close the fridge
Turn left then face the trash bin beside the fridge
Put the potato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled potato in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn left and go forward, then turn right at the fridge and go around to face the table.
Pick up the potato next to the cup, on the table.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Open the fridge, put the potato inside and chill it, and then take it out.
Go to the trash bin to the left of the fridge.
Put the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the trash.
